(c) 线圈自感

$$
L = \frac{N B \pi a^{2}}{I} = \frac{N^{2} \mu_{0} \mu \pi a^{2}}{\mu_{0} 2 \pi b + \mu W}
$$

故时间常数

$$
\begin{aligned}
\tau & = \frac{L}{R} = \frac{\frac{N^{2} \mu_{0} \mu \pi a^{2}}{\mu_{0} 2 \pi b + \mu W}}{\frac{\rho N 2 \pi a}{\pi r^{2}}} \\
& = \frac{N \mu_{0} \mu a \pi r^{2}}{2 \rho\left(\mu_{0} 2 \pi b + \mu W\right)}
\end{aligned}
$$
